{"tid":10241,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"陳日君：若梵蒂岡與中國建交　將「背叛耶穌基督」","createTime":"2016-11-29T00:46:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-07T17:37:39.000Z","uid":20933,"like":28,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"f82a621e5bb05496c032cec8fac7d116329260ed","tid":10241,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T00:46:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7J97LPx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7J97LPx.jpg&h=1dc7d356&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n天主教香港教區榮休主教陳日君樞機表示，若果梵蒂岡與中國達成邦交協議，將「背叛耶穌基督」。<br />\n<br />\n近期多次有消息傳出，中梵將就建交達成協議，84歲的陳日君接受英國《衛報》訪問時表示，梵蒂岡一旦與北京達成建交協議，將是「投降」，北京將介入天主教神職人員的任命。陳日君在報道中表示，支持中梵建交的人，不真正了解中國，缺乏對共產黨控制的教會的認識，他批評，官方主教不是真正在宣揚福音，而是如何服從共產黨當局，當民眾長期對教會失望之後，他們就會離開教會。<br />\n<br />\n陳日君又認為，神職人員應該站在民眾一邊，跟窮人和被迫害的人一起，而不是與政府為伍。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1299289-20161128.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1299289-20161128.htm&d=gHg%2Fa1kZgicCxdd1JZL7L5kBtgkcD0hE3Em2wkgk6m8%3D&h=a4a5dc60\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1299289-20161128.htm&h=47c68e90\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1299289-20161128.htm</a>"},{"pid":"c8ae536358e10024be2228a84d8d7ee715ab4f7a","tid":10241,"uid":37528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T00:52:57.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"d8db57ca0583ca3ae4efd9ab604313525393267f","tid":10241,"uid":37528,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T01:02:21.000Z","msg":"陳日君<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nbtw，下一任條仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=